Tsehe aer eth sorle ni eth Uanterl loer est. Yb feldatu, msot pleeop ihwt tsehe sorle aer ont srenisdi adn tndo' wni beads no eth 'aegms occnonlusi. Rof eemalxp, eth Tsejer nwis hwne ti deis.
wiki.category.minions.text:
Iminnso is a Loer Est ttha asnocitn sorle ciwhh wni ynol if wont eslos. Yeht aer ont aolyl ot yan occnonlusi. Yeht aelev eth agme if lla hreti simneee aer aedd. Yeht 'terna srenisdi ot yan orpug, os yeht tndo' amocmtcnuie ta ihtng.

Tsehe aer eth sorle ni eth Onimni loer est. Yb feldatu, msot pleeop ihwt tsehe sorle wni hwne wont eslos, adn aer ont srenisdi. If eth ynol aelrysp tlfe evali aer srdfine ihwt a onimni rpelay, ttha rpelay vlseea wont adn nwis.
wiki.category.cult.text: Tsehe aer eth sorle ni eth utcl loer est. Yb feldatu, msot pleeop ihwt tsehe sorle aer utcl lssaiyolt, utcl srenisdi, adn aer rtap fo eth Utcl yreharchi.
wiki.category.fiends.text: Tsehe aer eth sorle ni eth isndef loer est. Yb feldatu, msot pleeop ihwt tsehe sorle aer isndef lssaiyolt, tub ont srenisdi.
wiki.category.modifiers.text: Tsehe aer soonipt ttha nca eb dbenela ciwhh naecgh eth beorihva fo eth agme.
wiki.category.abilities.text: Iltsiabie aer ohw aelrysp emrfrop aiscotn ni eth agme. Ot ees ahwt aiscotn you nca kate, ees eth lbtiiay nemu. Eth Lbtiiay nemu is ehrwe eth errtlsonloc rof msot iltsiabie aer. Msot iltsiabie nahppe ta miithndg.
wiki.category.strategies.text: Eterh aer a tlo fo fpuelhl rsetgsatei ttha aelrysp seu ni rdeor ot lphe temh wni. Nwe rsetgsatei aer tarcede veeyr ayd.
wiki.category.menus.text: Tsehe aer fifedtrne nusme sued ot igve pintus ot eth agme.
wiki.category.phases.text:
Eth agme sha ayd sespah adn ihtng sespah
- Rgnuid eth ihtng sespah is tlcliyayp hwne aelrysp nca seu 'lrose iltsiabie adn get nnmiioftaro.
- Rgnuid eth ayd sespah, aelrysp csiusds nnmiioftaro yeht lerdnae adn evto no a rpelay ot klil rgnuid railt sespah.

Eth agme tlcliyayp atrsst ihwt a nebifrgi eapsh ot igve emit ot gfireu tuo ohw yoru loer kwsro, amnog eohtr ihnsgt. Fdrwtaaer, eth rdeor fo eth sespah fwsolol ihst lpoo: Skdu, Ihtng, Rytoauib, Indsocsusi, Inmntanooi, ehnt if a rpelay is maneontid Osytmtnie ocsem tenx, lldofoew yb Tedgumjen, adn if eth rpelay is ndouf uytigl eth tenx eapsh is Lniaf Wdsor, ehnt nfllyia, ti polso bakc uodarn ot Skdu. Eth agme nrsu ni ihst lpoo tlniu eterh is eon eamt egnimainr.

Tsehe aer eth sespah adn puorsg fo sespah ttha aer ni eth agme.
wiki.article.standard.mafia.title: Inctadesy Yreharchi
wiki.article.standard.mafia.text:
Eth inctadesy yreharchi is eth smtesy ciwhh seekp eth inctadesy egbni eabl ot klil veeyr ihtng. Eth inctadesy yreharchi is a lconciotle fo aelrysp owh aer yslauul salo inctadesy srenisdi adn inctadesy lssaiyolt. Eth smtesy fwsolol owt ulesr:
* If eterh is a Inctadesy Lnkgili loer ni eth yreharchi - hscu as Rfaheodtg or Tmosipro - hwne yeht die, theonra eembrm fo eth yreharchi lliw nteiirh hreti loer.
* If eterh is no Inctadesy Lnkgili loer ni eth yreharchi, a inctadesy eembrm is inevg eth inctadesy ugn. Hwne eth rpelay ihwt eth inctadesy ugn deis, theonra eembrm fo eth yreharchi rithsien ti.

Aelrysp ttha aer ni eth inctadesy yreharchi dten ot salo eb inctadesy srenisdi adn lssaiyolt. Ihst nmase yeht wni yb tiieinmlnga veeyr eohtr eamt adn nca talk tegretho rgnuid ihtng adn rytoauib.
wiki.article.standard.cult.title: Utcl Yreharchi
wiki.article.standard.cult.text:
Eth utcl yreharchi is eth smtesy ciwhh seekp eth utcl egbni eabl ot etehri klil or tnvecor heca ihtng. Eth utcl yreharchi is a lconciotle fo aelrysp owh aer yslauul salo utcl srenisdi adn utcl lssaiyolt. Eth utcl yreharchi aniinmsat 2 iltsiabie, klil adn tnvecor. Yeht tetraelna, cvtinnoger frtis, adn lnkgili eafrt.
* Eth utcl nca ynol klil eafrt yeht ehva sllucfssuyce ntoedvecr emoones. Eafrt ttha, yeht nca ynol tnvecor eafrt sllucfssuyce lnkgili emoones.
* If rof emso oasren a klil or tnvecor tseo'dn okrw (e.g. eth keilrl/novrceter swa celdobk), ehnt eth esam lbtiiay is reitd ingaa eth tenx ihtng - ti tseo'dn wthisc. Ebauesc fo ihst, lnkgili/cvtinnoger is ont nrlyieenth "veeyr eohtr ihtng".

Tsehe aer ohw eth utcl sorle eeeuctx eth seudti fo eth utcl:
* Solepta: Eth utcl yreharchi untgearesa eterh is sylaaw an solepta. If eth solepta deis, eth rpelay owh sha neeb ni eth utcl yreharchi eth sgteoln cmeseob eth solepta. Eth estpla'os lbtiiay is ot tnvecor aelrysp, eowrvhe if eterh is no otleaz, ehnt eth solepta sklil.
* Cdepiils: Eth cdepiils sha no lbtiiay. A cdepiils yma ecboem an solepta if eth solepta deis.
* Otleaz: Eth rpelay owh sha neeb ni eth utcl yreharchi eth tssrheto is eth ynol otleaz. If eterh is a otleaz, ti lliw emrfrop lginilsk taherr ntha eth solepta.
wiki.article.standard.whisper.title: Rhwisep
wiki.article.standard.whisper.text:
Rgnuid eth ayd, as nglo as you nca kspae ni lla ahct, you nca rhwisep ot yan eohtr iigvln rpelay
- Inwrshepig dssne a ievaprt ahct seesmag ot eth rpelay you csohe
- Ot rhwisep emoones, seu eth rhwisep cmmando or noep eth rhwisep necanlh giusn eth ntbout ni eth tslayilrep
   - Eth rhwisep cmmando is "\w#" ehrwe "#" is drelcape ihwt eth rpelay buenrm fo eth rpelay you atnw ot rhwisep, os "\2w Hey, my loer is hitwc!" ipehssrw ot rpelay @2
- Hwne you rhwisep emoones, a seesmag is tesn ni lla ahct siagyn ttha you dsiprheew ot eth rpelay you csohe, os rneeeyov snowk ttha you dsiprheew ttha rpelay
 - You t'nca rhwisep ot an cnasdiefrhne rpelay
 - If you try ot dnes an ailnidv rhwisep you aer tesn a ahct seesmag siagyn ttha you ctna rhwisep.
wiki.article.standard.tag.title: Tga
wiki.article.standard.tag.text: Gats aer ocins sohnw tenx ot rpelay namse ni eth rpelay nemu. Gats nca eb eaddd or dvoeemr yb emso sorle. Gats nca swoh nnmiioftaro elik owh eth gadrstehfo upkcab is, owh is eth Eyiuarrolvnto trgaet, owh eth nmiactroi sha agdegt, etc. Aelrysp aer told hwne yeht iagn adn sleo gats no eohtr aelrysp.
wiki.article.standard.reveal.title: Vreael
wiki.article.standard.reveal.text:
- Hwne a rpelay is elrdeaev ot you, you nca ees hreti loer lbael, adn you aer inevg a seesmag siagyn hreti loer
- Hwne a rpelay is lnaeoedcc mofr you, you sleo hreti loer lbael, adn aer inevg a ahct seesmag siagyn yeht aer lnaeoedcc fmro you
    - A rpelay sgte lnaeoedcc hwne yeht die or wthisc sorle.

 Eelnagrvi adn loer belals aer ievaprt. os if you ees a loer lbael, sretoh thimg ont salo ees ttha loer lbael. Srenisdi aer sylaaw elrdeaev ot heca eohtr. of__r Xa__eeplm inctadesy.
wiki.article.standard.roleLabel.title: Loer Lbael
wiki.article.standard.roleLabel.text:
- Loer belals eaparp tenx ot rpelay namse, ti wsosh ahwt loer ttha rpelay is
- Loer belals aer ont sylaaw plbuic, rof eemalxp, you nca ees yoru onw loer lbael ta lla mties, tub eohtr aelrysp nca ont
- A inctadesy eembrm nca ees eth eohtr inctadesy meremsb loer belals
- Hwne you iagn a loer lbael no theonra rpelay, you get a ahct seesmag siagyn ttha aelrysp loer swa elrdeaev ot you
- Hwne you sleo a loer lbael no theonra rpelay, you get a ahct seesmag siagyn ttha aelrysp loer swa lnaeoedcc mofr you
- If a rpelay ttha is elrdeaev ot you ishswcet sorle or deis, hreti loer lbael lliw eb lnaeoedcc
- Aedd aelrysp nca ont ehva loer belals, eth loer ttha sapprea tenx ot hreti eanm is jtus eth loer no hreti eravg. Tsehe nca eb enaciutacr rof asnores elik eth nmiactroi or srrego'f lbtiiay
wiki.category.trial.text:
Eth railt sespah occur eafrt indsocsusi adn ned bfeero skdu, adn aer eth sespah ni ciwhh aelrysp nca eb tdove pu adn tdove tuo.

Eth railt sespah go ni ihst rdeor:
- Inmntanooi
- Osytmtnie
- Tedgumjen
- Lniaf Wdsor

A rpelay is maneontid eafrt tengitg tdove pu yb rome ntha fhla fo eth iigvln aelrysp.
Eafrt egbni maneontid, rgnuid osytmtnie, ynol eth maneontid rpelay nca kspae os yeht nca ededfn vehsetmsel.
Eafrt osytmtnie, rgnuid tedgumjen, rneeeyov oesvt etehri uytigl or oitnncen. If eterh aer rome uytigl oesvt ntha oitnncen oesvt, eth agme oegs ot lniaf wdsor. Ihtsoeewr, ti oegs bakc ot inmntanooi if eterh aer alisrt tlfe, or seel ti oegs ot skdu.
Rgnuid lniaf wdsor, eth rpelay owh swa tdove uytigl ysas hreti slta uhtothgs bfeero egbni llikde yb uictnoxee.
Eterh nca ynol eb pu ot 3 inmntanooi sespah erp ayd. If 3 alisrt nahppe adn no rpelay is euctdexe, skdu atrsst.
wiki.article.standard.interview.title: Enietrwvi
wiki.article.standard.interview.text: A erroretp nca enietrwvi a rpelay rgnuid eth ihtng, ogwlialn eth erroretp ot kspae ihwt temh. Eth rpelay egbni evditeewnir yma ont wonk owh eth erroretp is, tub rneeeyov snowk eth erroretp is no eth wont eamt.
wiki.article.standard.report.title: Erprto
wiki.article.standard.report.text: Eth erroretp sha a erprto ciwhh is tepods ilylbupc veeyr rytoauib eth erroretp eoohscs ot. Rneeeyov snowk eth erprto swa irwttne yb eth erroretp os yeht wonk eth nnmiioftaro is suwttyhrtor. Eth erroretp yma enietrwvi a rpelay heca ihtng ot iagn nnmiioftaro ot lducien ni eth erprto.
wiki.article.standard.forged.title: Orfeg
wiki.article.standard.forged.text: A rpelay owh is ferdgo had hreti ibila adn loer hecagnd yb eth roerfg no hreti eravg.
wiki.article.standard.visit.title: Vstii
wiki.article.standard.visit.text:
Vtisis aer eth erco fo eth agme
- Aelrysp nca vstii eohtr aelrysp ot seu hreti iltsiabie
- Tlcliyayp, icsnghoo a rpelay ihwt a loer lbtiiay ucessa you ot vstii eth hsnoce rpelay, aouhlhgt eterh aer  pcexoseitn
- Vtisis estor aadt
    - Ritsovi (Rpelay)
    - Trgaet (Rpelay)
    - Ctniatgak (reut/easlf)
    - Tstparnro inumme (reut/easlf)
    - Oablwdcrk inumme (reut/easlf)
    - Itrednic (reut/easlf)
         - Itrednic ucessa eth vstii ot ont ricatnte ihwt nyma eohtr iltsiabie. An itrednic ritsovi is ont tekacatd yb rtsnaeev, samasnmkr, pcso, rolipksys, mhsaurbse, nnegsreie, or ewrselovew. Itrednic vtisis do ont auces a nosop ot get ctna ltle or auces eth ritsovi ot get eusddo yb an srosnait.

 Hree aer emso lmpxease fo ohw vtisis thimg okrw
- @7 is a Tcevetdei owh eoohscs @17, os @7 vtisis @17 adn asenlr a eutsrl batuo @17
 No eth esam ihtng @01 is a tuokool owh salo eoohscs @17. Os @01 asenlr ttha @7 sditeiv hreti trgaet.
- Eterh is vengaliti, owh eoohscs ot hsoot @03. Ta eth esam emit, eterh is an enngeeri owh sha hreti tapr est no @03. Eth nnegsreie tapr sklil eth vengaliti ebauesc eth vengaliti is invtisig @03 ihwt an ctniatgak vstii
- A vtisis trgaet nca eb hecagnd utihwot eth ritsovi eenv onigwnk, rof eemalxp, eth iltsiabie fo Nretorsatpr, Repwar, adn Hitwc auces vtisis atretsg ot naecgh.
wiki.article.standard.target.title: Trgaet
wiki.article.standard.target.text:
Yoru trgaet is eth rpelay owh you vstii.
- A vstii tgatriegn emoones nmase ttha eth ritsovi is invtisig ttha rpelay.
wiki.article.standard.hypnotize.title: Zhyetopni
wiki.article.standard.hypnotize.text: A rpelay owh is eoyhnitdzp swa a yphsontits trgaet. Yeht ylliepttnoa aer told a fake seesmag mofr eth ntiyhspot. Yeht yma ehva neeb eordobcelkl.
wiki.article.standard.frame.title: Efram
wiki.article.standard.frame.text: A rpelay owh is rafmed swa a seafrmr trgaet.
wiki.article.standard.convert.title: Tnvecor
wiki.article.standard.convert.text:
A lre'spya loer is hecagnd. Lla fo hreti lbtiiay uses aer feelirdl ot iummamx. fOr_ Eemalxp:_
- If emoones is ntoedvecr ot a Aevntre, yeht get lla etehr lbtiiay uses.
- An Solepta nca tnvecor aelrysp toni stltiucs.
wiki.article.standard.roleblock.title: Rloekocbl
wiki.article.standard.roleblock.text: A rpelay owh is eordobcelkl sha hreti vtisis eadser. A lre'spya vtisis egbni eadser tfone nmase yeht t'nca seu hreti lbtiiay. Emso sorle aer inumme or ont defctafe yb egbni eordobcelkl. Roects, Tosnocr, adn Ntiyhspot aer sorle ttha nca rloekocbl eohtr aelrysp adn aer hotb inumme ot egbni eordobcelkl.
wiki.article.standard.ward.title: Adwr
wiki.article.standard.ward.text:
Emoones nca eb eardwd. Aeonyn owh vtisis a rpelay owh is eardwd sha lla hreti vtisis eadser adn eisceevr a ahct seesmag siagyn ttha yeht aer blrcedwdkoa. fOr_ El_pemax:
- A ceunbro lsstece a rpelay ot adwr heca ihtng
- Eth orjlia stpu a rpelay ni ljai, irdwgan temh.

 Emso sorle aer oablwdcrk inumme
- A tsejer nca klil emoones eenv if rhey'te eardwd
wiki.article.standard.block.title: Olbck
wiki.article.standard.block.text: A rpelay owh is celdobk swa etehri eordobcelkl, blrcedwdkoa, or hotb. A rpelay i'nst celdobk if rhey'te inumme
wiki.article.standard.detain.title: Edtnia
wiki.article.standard.detain.text:
A rpelay owh is eentidda ta ihtng:
- Is eardwd mofr lla vtisis.
- Is eordobcelkl.
- Sha hreti lbtiiay deaacitvdet.
- Temh adn hreti fwlleo srenisdi aer told yeht aer eentidda ta eth rsatt fo ihtng.

Emso lmpxease fo sorle ttha nca edtnia aelrysp aer: Orjlia, adn Kippradne.
Wdaern seod ont edtnia aelrysp.
wiki.article.standard.rampage.title: Gpaerma
wiki.article.standard.rampage.text: Lla viirssto ot a apadgrem rpelay aer ndcieyritl tekacatd. Eth gpaerma seasrh eth ctkata elvle fo eth arpgamgni thcaarerc.
wiki.article.standard.possess.title: Sosssep
wiki.article.standard.possess.text:
A rpelay nca eb esesospds toni theonra rpelay, nfgcori temh ot seu hreti lbtiiay a atincre ayw.
- Esesospds aelrysp aer told yeht aer esesospds tub ont told owh yeht aer esesospds toni, onr aer yeht told ahwt hreti lbtiiay is fcrdeo toni gidno.
- Iltsiabie t'nca eb fcrdeo toni hsotimgne ttha yeht tlcliyayp t'nca do (ie, a tcevetdei atnnoc eb fcrdeo ot asgtetviine tesmlfeh, ebauesc a tcevetdei is ont eabl ot asgtetviine vehsetmsel tlcliyayp)
- Emso iltsiabie aer inumme ot sonipssoes, tub yeht aer itlls told yeht aer esesospds.

Ihst is ohw heca rolencorlt ptye is fteeecfd hwne you aer esesospds:
- Hceockbx: If you aer esesospds toni yslfoeru, eth oxb is oecrf ecechkd, ihtsoeewr iognthn hepasnp.
- Rpelay Slti: Eth slti fo aelrysp (or eth iselng rpelay tlso) is est ot niatnoc ynol eth rpelay you aer esesospds toni.
- Lxeayct Owt Aelrysp: Eth frtis rpelay oceich is est ot eth rpelay you aer esesospds toni, tub eth ceosnd rpelay oceich stsya as ahwt ti swa rolginyial est ot.

 Lla udslinet errtlsonloc aer dneecfufet yb sonipssoes. Errtlsonloc t'nca eb est ot an ailnidv oceich.
wiki.article.standard.defense.title: Fdeenes
wiki.article.standard.defense.text:
Aktatcs adn fdeenes ehva 3 siter heca. An ctkata nca etehri eb absic, mrpga-rciroeni, or iirppotecogerintc-n.

A fdeenes nca etehri eb arredom, eectdprot, or envbilniic.

A absic ctkata nca ont klil a rpelay owh is arredom, adn an mrpga-rciroeni ctkata nca ont klil a rpelay owh is eectdprot. A iirppotecogerintc-n ctkata nca eowrvrepo oamrr as well as pooencrtti.

 Emso sorle ehva oamrr yb feldatu, yslauul veil osne. Pooencrtti nca eb naergtd ot aelrysp ohhgutr iltsiabie elik eth Sd'otcor lbtiiay ot dagru hreti trgaet. A rpelay ihwt envbilniic fdeenes nca ynol die yb tengitg euctdexe or lnaevgi eth agme.

Ssnelu ihtsoeewr dicndiaet, aktatcs aer absic yb feldatu adn lliw ont eb eabl ot klil aelrysp owh aer arredom or eectdprot. Itrednic is ont a iret fo ctkata.
wiki.article.standard.guard.title: Dagru
wiki.article.standard.guard.text:
A rpelay nca dagru theonra rpelay
- Eth dedagru rpelay sha eectdprot fdeenes rof eth ihtng.
- If eth dedagru rpelay is tekacatd:
    - Eth dedagru rpelay is told yeht ehva neeb dedagru mofr ta astel eon ctkata.
    - Eth rpelay owh is gugdnari eth dedagru rpelay is told yeht dedagru a rpelay mofr ta astel eon ctkata.
wiki.article.standard.fragileVest.title: Feialrg Tves
wiki.article.standard.fragileVest.text:
A rpelay ihwt a feialrg tves sha fdeenes tlniu yeht aer tekacatd rgnuid miithndg.
 - A rpelay nca ehva lmitleup feialrg vsets ta eocn
 - Heca tves esvig a fifedtrne fdeenes prewo.
 - A tves ksbrea no eth ihtng eth rpelay ihwt eth tves is tekacatd
 - Heca tves ocsem ihwt a est fo aelrysp, tsehe aelrysp aer told hwne eth tves ksbrea. Eth rpelay owh sha eth tves is ont esyalcneisr told ttha yeht ehva a tves or ttha eth tves kbeor.
wiki.article.standard.dead.title: Aedd
wiki.article.standard.dead.text:
Hwne a rpelay deis:
- Hreti eravg is eaddd ot eth aagvrdrye

Helwi a rpelay is aedd:
- Msot fo hreti iltsiabie tndo' okrw
- Yeht t'nca evto
- Yeht t'nca ahct ni lla ahct
- Yeht nca ahct ni aedd ahct.
wiki.article.standard.silenced.title: Sniceel
wiki.article.standard.silenced.text:
A rpelay owh is enldeisc nca ont talk or ihtsoeewr amocmtcnuie rgnuid ttha ayd.
- Yeht nca itlls evto rgnuid eth tedgumjen eapsh
- If eth enldeisc rpelay is tpu no railt, yeht itlls t'nca talk
- If eth aelrysp aer laingkt tuo olud, enldeisc aelrysp hodsul ont kspae or seu yan ptye fo oonincuctmmia, gludnicin lsnsagi or ciflaa rssispexeno. Eth eulr is, fo a rpelay t'nca seu ahct, yeht aer ont dleowla ot amocmtcnuie
- Sorle elik eupdyt yramo adn orjlia nca itlls seu hreti iltsiabie mlornlay rgnuid eth ayd eenv if enldeisc

 A Iacraebllkm nca sniceel a rpelay heca ihtng.
wiki.article.standard.friends.title: Srdfine
wiki.article.standard.friends.text:
If 2 aelrysp nca wni eth esam agme, yeht aer srdfine.
 - A tsejer nca wni ni eth esam agme as a tcevetdei, os yeht aer srdfine
- An Solepta nca wni ni eth esam agme as a cdepiils os yeht aer srdfine
- A rfaheodtg t'nca wni ni eth esam agme as a tcevetdei, yeht hotb deen eth eohtr ot sleo, os yeht aer simneee
- A aetoeintrm is srdfine ihwt a prteeupep adn simneee ihwt a eduimm
 Eth ppsehohorli, tcevetdei, adn sgopis, nca seu hreti iltsiabie ot ees if pleeop aer srdfine or simneee, aouhlhgt uaasr nca etfcfe tsehe ruestsl.

 A rpelay nca salo eb srdfine ihwt ncocinslsou. If you nca wni ihwt wont ehnt you aer srdfine ihwt wont, rof eemalxp, a tcevetdei is srdfine ihwt wont tub simneee ihwt inctadesy.
wiki.article.standard.enemies.title: Simneee
wiki.article.standard.enemies.text:
If 2 aelrysp deen eth eohtr ot sleo ni rdeor rof vehsetmsel ot wni, yeht aer simneee.
- A Litpoicina t'nca wni nlsdgoiea a yramo, os yeht aer simneee.
- A rfaheodtg t'nca wni ni eth esam agme as a orjlia, os yeht aer simneee.
- A tsejer nca wni ni eth esam agme as a tcevetdei, os yeht aer srdfine.
- An Solepta t'nca wni ihwt a rfaheodtg, os yeht aer simneee.

 Eth ppsehohorli, tcevetdei, adn sgopis, nca seu hreti iltsiabie ot ees if pleeop aer srdfine or simneee, aouhlhgt uaasr nca etfcfe tsehe ruestsl.
wiki.article.standard.loyalist.title: Lylasiot
wiki.article.standard.loyalist.text:
A rpelay owh is a lylasiot nwis if adn ynol if eth occnonlusi hreti aolyl ot is cehrdae.
 - A Tcevetdei is yslauul a wont lylasiot
 -  A Tsejer is yslauul ont aolyl ot yan wni oninticod, hreti wni oninticod is tpnnedeinde, (Eenv if yeht aer srdfine ihwt wont, yeht 'terna a wont lylasiot).

 Aelrysp owh aer aolyl ot fifedtrne ncocinslsou utsm eb simneee.
 Aelrysp nca ynol eb aolyl ot agme ncocinslsou
 - "Tsejer" i'nst a occnonlusi os eterh is no "Tsejer Lylasiot".
wiki.article.standard.insider.title: Eniidrs
wiki.article.standard.insider.text:
An eniidrs orpug is a orpug fo aelrysp owh ehva eth loinolgfw eeiptrspor
 - Yeht ehva eth loer fo lla eohtr iigvln srenisdi ni hreti orpug elrdeaev ot temh
 - Yeht ehva a ihtng ahct orpug ihwt lla eohtr iigvln srenisdi

 Rof eemalxp, A caitlpy Rfaheodtg is a Inctadesy Eniidrs, yeht ehva eth sorle fo lla inctadesy srenisdi elrdeaev adn nca talk ot temh ta ihtng.
 Noaitrmstee aer Prteeupep Srenisdi
 Ciedteestv aer ont tfone Wont Srenisdi ebauesc yeht tndo' ehva a ihtng ahct or ehva lla wont srenisdi elrdeaev ot temh.
 Theonra eanm rof eniidrs is "eembrm". A rpelay is a inctadesy eniidrs or inctadesy eembrm if yeht aer ni eth inctadesy eniidrs orpug
Emso lmpxease fo eniidrs puorsg aer:
    - Inctadesy
    - Utcl
    - Prteeupep
wiki.article.standard.conclusion.title: Occnonlusi
wiki.article.standard.conclusion.text:
Eth agme ynol dnes hwne a occnonlusi is deceddi. Msot aelrysp wni niintsdooc lliw edpend no eth occnonlusi deceddi.
- Emso lmpxease fo ncocinslsou aer:
    - Wont
    - Inctadesy
    - Utcl
    - Isndef
    - Icne Slti
    - Arwd

- A agme occnonlusi is tdnmieeder cgroiancd ot eth loinolgfw ulesr
    - If lla aelrysp owh aer *tdnoecu rof eth agme occnonlusi hkcec* aer srdfine ihwt a occnonlusi, ttha occnonlusi nwis.
        - If eterh aer no aelrysp egnimainr, eth agme dnes ni a arwd
    - A rpelay is ynol *tdnoecu rof eth agme occnonlusi hkcec* if yan fo eth loinolgfw is reut
        - Hreti loer is ni eth inctadesy lnkgili loer est, or hreti loer is ni eth isndef loer est
        - Yeht aer a wont lylasiot
        - Yeht aer a inctadesy eniidrs
wiki.article.standard.role.title: Loer
wiki.article.standard.role.text:
Veeyr rpelay sha a loer. Hreti loer iedsneemrt ahwt hreti lbtiiay is.
 of__r eemalxp:__ Aifomso is a loer ihwt eth lbtiiay ot klil a rpelay heca ihtng.
 Yb feldatu, a Loer iedsneemrt ahwt a aelrysp wni oninticod is, adn ahwt yeht puorsg yeht aer srenisdi ni. Eowrvhe, ihst nca naecgh ued ihnsgt hscu as prteeupep ngnchiga a aelrysp wni oninticod tub ont hreti loer.
wiki.article.standard.haunt.title: Hnatu
wiki.article.standard.haunt.text: Eafrt yeht die, a Eduimm nca hnatu a iigvln rpelay ot woall temh ot amocmtcnuie ihwt eth aedd rgnuid eth ihtng. Eth huentda rpelay is eaddd ot eth aedd ahct orpug ta ihtng. If lmitleup mmiudse hnatu lmitleup aelrysp, yeht nca lla kspae ihwt heca eohtr adn lla aedd aelrysp.
wiki.article.standard.transport.title: Tstparnro
wiki.article.standard.transport.text:
Ta miithndg, aelrysp nca eb aprstetndor. Hwne a rpelay is aprstetndor:
- Eth aprstetndor rpelay is told yeht aer aprstetndor.
- Lla vtisis ot eth aprstetndor rpelay aer edetdcrrei ot theonra rpelay.

Eon tstparnro lbtiiay nca tstparnro lmitleup aelrysp.
- A vstii nca ont eb aprstetndor yb a iselng lbtiiay rome ntha eocn.
- Eafrt a tstparnro lbtiiay hepasnp, eth vtisis aestadosci ihwt ttha lbtiiay nca ont eb edetdcrrei yb theonra tstparnro.
wiki.article.standard.obscured.title: Sorubce
wiki.article.standard.obscured.text: A rpelay owh is rsceubod had hreti loer adn ibila eadser mofr hreti eravg. A Nmiactroi nca tga aelrysp rof oisrungcb, ehnt hwne yeht die, yeht aer rsceubod.
wiki.article.standard.evil.title: Veil
wiki.article.standard.evil.text: If a loer is veil, ti nmase a loer is t-ononnw. A pcscyhi nca ivercee veil osnivsi ot lnera owh is ont no wont. A tcevetdei lliw ees emoones as ispuiossuc if yeht aer veil or ehva a ispuiossuc raua.
wiki.article.standard.roleLimit.title: Loer Ilmit
wiki.article.standard.roleLimit.text:
A sorle ilmit is eth iummamx buenrm fo ttha loer ttha nca eb rtaegeden ta eth rsatt fo a rgraleu agme. If eterh is no ilmit, eterh nca eb yan buenrm fo ttha loer.
- Aevntre sha a loer ilmit fo 1, eterh nca ynol eb eon aevntre, if 2 pleeop mailc aevntre, eon utsm eb nligy
- Rdcwiadl utsm edaher ot loer ilmit
wiki.article.standard.douse.title: Oesud
wiki.article.standard.douse.text: Rssoasitn nca oesud aelrysp, ehnt aetlr iegnit, ot ctkata rneeeyov owh is eusddo. If eterh is an srosnait evali ehnt eusddo aelrysp ehva a ispuiossuc raua. Inntiigg is an itrednic, iirppotecogerintc-n ctkata ot lla eusddo aelrysp.
wiki.article.standard.spiral.title: Rsilap
wiki.article.standard.spiral.text: UIMUKAZ nca ntiuefaat aelrysp, ciwhh ucessa temh ot rsilap. Ngrailisp aelrysp aer ont told yeht aer ngrailisp, adn yeht die eth tenx ihtng. Viirssto ot ngrailisp aelrysp rsatt ot rsilap. Gdiyn ued ot ngrailisp is an itrednic, mrpga-rciroeni ctkata.
wiki.article.standard.backup.title: Upkcab
wiki.article.standard.backup.text:
Eth inctadesy nca escooh a rpelay ot eb eth upkcab. If lla eth inctadesy lnkgili iltsiabie aer celdobk, ehnt eth upkcab aktatcs hreti trgaet indsate indsate.
- Eth upkcab nca teslec a fifedtrne trgaet mofr eth eohtr lnkgili lbtiiay
- Eth eohtr lnkgili lbtiiay udocl eb a inctadesy lnkgili loer or a rpelay ihwt eth ugn
wiki.article.standard.confused.title: Uncseofd
wiki.article.standard.confused.text:
Eth loer fo a rpelay owh is uncseofd thimg ont cnntuoif lrecyotrc. Uncseofd eastcff heca loer eyrefnlitdf. You thimg ont eb told ttha you aer uncseofd.
 Ohw ihst eastcff veeyr loer:
   - Nosop: You aer sylaaw told ttha you t'nca ltle
   - Tcevetdei: You aer sylaaw told oitnncen
   - Ppsehohorli: You aer sylaaw told srdfine
   - Sgopis: You aer sylaaw told ttha yoru trgaet did'tn vstii an yeenm
   - Pcscyhi: You aer told a dnarmo slti fo 3 aelrysp rof yoru veil ionsiv, You aer told a dnarmo slti fo 2 aelrysp rof yoru ogdo ionsiv.
 - Lytal Eklrc: You aer told etehri 1 rome or 1 lses ntha eth ctrerco buenrm you hodsul eb told. If ti ulwdo eecedx eth buenrm fo aelrysp owh tdove uytigl, ti is ttha buenrm indsate. If ti reew ot go erndu 0, ti is 0 indsate.
 - Oautidr: You get dnarmo sorle, yeht thimg eb ctrerco or rnreioctc. You aer ynol told sorle ttha udocl ehva cmeo mofr ttha tlso.
wiki.article.standard.marionette.title: Rtnisg Pu
wiki.article.standard.marionette.text:
A rpelay owh is a aetoeintrm sha ejniod a fifedtrne eamt
- Yeht peke hreti dol loer hwne yeht ecboem a aetoeintrm
- Yeht aer tekacatd veeyr ihtng yb eth loer ttha teidcreur temh ihwt a pooencrtti grnepici ctkata(EX. Ueretcirr or Prteeupep)
- If eterh aer no aelrysp ihwt eth loer ttha teidcreur temh, eth aetoeintrm is itlls tekacatd
- Eth aetoeintrm no lenogr nwis ihwt hreti garioinl eamt tub nwis ihwt eth nwe eamt indsate
wiki.article.standard.aura.title: Raua
wiki.article.standard.aura.text:
An raua is a atstus etfcfe tpu no a rpelay ttha ucessa temh ot seegrrit eyrefnlitdf ot aiintvtigeves iltsiabie.
 - Rof eemalxp, a Tcevetdei sees yan aelrysp ihwt a ispuiossuc raua as simneee ot wont, eenv if yeht aer srdfine ihwt wont
 - Ot wonk ohw oitnncen raua or ispuiossuc raua thimg etfcfe an lbtiiay, ot go eth lunmaa pgae rof ttha loer.

 Hree aer lmpxease fo iltsiabie ttha thimg auces a rpelay ot ehva an raua.
 - Afemrr esvig a rpelay ispuiossuc raua rof a ihtng
 - Gadrstehfo ehva an oitnncen raua, eenv if rhey'te eordobcelkl
 - Iisedgsur nca igve a rpelay an oitnncen raua rof eon ihtng

If a rpelay sha hotb an oitnncen adn ispuiossuc raua ta eth esam emit, eth ispuiossuc raua *yslauul* redivreso.
 - A rpelay ihwt an oitnncen raua adn a ispuiossuc raua eetsisgrr as simneee ihwt wont cgroiancd ot a tcevetdei
wiki.article.standard.appearedVisit.text:
A rpelay udocl par_a_pe ot ehva sditeiv emoones, eenv hguhot yeht did'tn. Ihst is yslauul ducesa yb veil sorle hscu as Afemrr.

Ihst ynol eastcff aiintvtigeves sorle.

ePa_xesl_m

Eth Krrctae adn Tuokool nca ees eth dpaapere vstii, tub ont eth rale vstii.

A Aevntre tseo'dn ctkata a rpelay owh dpaapere ot vstii temh adn did'tn utlyaacl vstii temh.
wiki.article.standard.roleOutline.title: Loer Lnoutie
wiki.article.standard.roleOutline.text:
A loer lnoutie esnifed a orpug fo sorle.

Sutoienl nca etehri eb a fiedneredp loer est, an etcxa loer, or a onnui fo lmitleup.

ePa_xesl_m

"Yan" Ti udocl eb yan loer

"Uanterl" Udocl eb yan sbesolpi uanterl loer.

"Wont Pousprt" Udocl eb an Roects, Iobittirursten, Nretorsatpr, or Eduimm

"Rfaheodtg" Udocl ynol eb a Rfaheodtg.

"Rdcwiadl ∪ Pcscyhi" Udocl etehri eb an Rdcwiadl or Pcscyhi.

- Hwne sorle aer rtaegeden anrymdlo mofr a loer lnoutie, heca sbesolpi loer is lyuelqa llkeiy ot neagtere.
- Loer sutoienl aer sued ni eth lnoutie slti ot swoh ahwt sorle udocl eb ni eth agme.
wiki.article.standard.outlineList.title: Lnoutie Slti
wiki.article.standard.outlineList.text:
Eth lnoutie slti esnifed ahwt sorle aer ni eth agme. Hwne eth agme atrsst:
- Heca loer lnoutie eegantesr a dnarmo loer mofr eth sorle ni eth lnoutie
- Heca rpelay is eanissgd ot a loer lnoutie, adn hrtoeeefr a loer.
wiki.article.standard.chatGroup.title: Ahct Orpug
wiki.article.standard.chatGroup.text:
Lla gmesasse aer etehri ievaprt or tesn eon fo tsehe ahct puorsg

wiki.article.standard.fastForward.title: Satf Fwardor
wiki.article.standard.fastForward.text: If lla iigvln aelrysp evto ot satf fwardor, eth cuernrt eapsh ylttninsa dnes. Otnvgi ot satf fwardor is oteyplmcle unoynosam, noybod eenv snowk hwne you srspe eth ntbout. Ot evto ot satf fwardor, noep eth satf fwardor dpro ndwo ni eth opt tlfe. You nca etehri escooh ot satf fwardor eth cuernrt eapsh, or ot satf fwardor ot a cscepfii eapsh.
wiki.article.standard.told.title: Told
wiki.article.standard.told.text: If you aer told hsotimgne, you reew tesn a ahct seesmag sattnig ti.
wiki.article.standard.howToPlay.title: Ohw Ot Ypal
wiki.article.standard.howToPlay.text:
Eth galo fo eth agme deepnds no yoru loer. Msot sorle wni if lla aelrysp mofr ispongop aestm aer malnetieid
Eth aestm aer Wont, Inctadesy, Utcl, Isndef
- Wont hodsul try ot dnfi tuo owh eth inctadesy is ni rdeor ot evto temh tuo
- Inctadesy, utcl, adn isndef, hodsul try ot ysta hidnde helwi lnkgili oswtien

Eth agme nrsu ni sespah fo ayd adn ihtng
- Rgnuid ihtng, heca rpelay uses hreti sorle iltsiabie
- Rgnuid eth ayd, aelrysp csiusds nnmiioftaro yeht lerdnae adn evto no a rpelay ot klil

Eterh aer upashbses hinwti ayd adn ihtng

# Ihtng
Msot loer iltsiabie okrw ta ihtng. Hree aer emso lmpxease
- Heca ihtng, eth rfaheodtg nca teslec a rpelay ot klil temh
- Heca ihtng, eth tcevetdei nca teslec a rpelay. Eth tcevetdei is told if eth rpelay yeht teslec is oitnncen or ispuiossuc. Ihst ulwdo lphe eth tcevetdei dnfi tuo owh eth inctadesy is. If yeht aer ispuiossuc yeht aer a wont yeenm
- Heca ihtng, eth afemrr nca teslec a rpelay ot amek temh seegrrit syelfla ot eth tcevetdei. Os a wiento udocl seegrrit as ispuiossuc ot a tcevetdei syelfla if a afemrr sued hreti lbtiiay

# Rytoauib
Rgnuid eth rytoauib eapsh, rneeeyov is told owh ided, nloag ihwt eth loer adn ibila fo oesth owh ided.
Lla aelrysp hodsul peke hreti ibila teon pgae ot peke ktrca fo lla eth nnmiioftaro yeht lerdnae rgnuid eth agme. Eth rytoauib eapsh is a pectfre emit ot ewitr ndwo ni yoru ibila ahwt you lerdnae slta ihtng. Rof eemalxp:

- If uoe'yr a tcevetdei owh lerdnae ttha @5 is ispuiossuc no ihtng 1. You udocl ewitr yoru ibila ot oklo elik ihst

Tcevetdei
Ihtng 1: @5 - ispuiossuc

Ti is salo iapnotrtm rof onn wiento aelrysp ot peke a fake ibila ot pnertde ttha yeht aer a wiento

# Indsocsusi
Eth indsocsusi eapsh is ehrwe aelrysp csiusds eth nnmiioftaro yeht lerdnae adn try ot dnfi tuo owh eth inctadesy, isndef, adn utcl aer
Aelrysp lliw ksa heca eohtr ot mailc, ihst nmase yeht atnw ot wonk eth nnmiioftaro ttha eth eohtr rpelay lerdnae
Msot aelrysp dnes hreti ibila ni ahct rgnuid ihst eapsh, ot hersa eth nnmiioftaro lycetffinie ni oepersns ot egbni saked ot mailc. Ti lliw llkeiy eb iedcnsedor ispuiossuc ot ont ehva an ibila ppdraere hwne saked rof eon. Os tis rvey iapnotrtm ot ehva eon ppdraere, no tteram owh you aer

# Inmntanooi
Rgnuid inmntanooi, aelrysp nca evto eohtr aelrysp no ot railt ni rdeor ot eeeuctx temh
Eth sebt ayw rof oswtien ot klil inctadesy meremsb is ot seu hreti evto, eenv if you eran’t atincre emoones is veil, otnvgi temh oont railt adn tgeirnthnae temh lliw tfone igve nnmiioftaro ot lphe dnfi inctadesy
- If rome ntha fhla fo eth iigvln aelrysp evto rof eon rpelay, ttha rpelay is tpu no railt
- If eterh eran’t oguhne oesvt ni emit, eth agme sipks lrytecdi ot skdu

# Osytmtnie
- Eth rpelay tdove no rital is eth ynol rpelay dleowla ot kspae adn ahct rgnuid ihst eapsh, yeht hodsul alnirecyt mailc, dnes hreti ibila adn ysa ahwt hreti loer is

# Tedgumjen
- Rneeeyov oesvt oitnncen or uytigl (or nbstasia)
- If rome aelrysp evto uytigl ntha oitnncen, eth rpelay no railt lliw eb euctdexe
- If eth rpelay no railt sin’t euctdexe, eterh is theonra rital (ihwt a axm fo etehr)

# Lniaf wdsor
- Eth rpelay owh swa no railt hodsul eb dleowla ot ysa emso lniaf wdsor or otnse yeht ehva rof eth wont

# Skdu
- A ne-thgrpi eapsh rof rneeeyov ot get a slta odwr ni bfeero eth tenx ihtng

# Lniaf uhtothgs
Eth agme nrsu ni ihst lpoo tlniu eterh is eon eamt egnimainr
Eth miithndg lunmaa sha a slti fo lla sorle adn hreti iltsiabie. Ti is dmeemocndre ot dear pu no yoru loer rgnuid eth gnnbgenii nebifrgi eapsh
If yoru veil, you hodsul try ot lnera ohw ta astel eon wiento loer kwsro os you nca pnertde ot eb ttha loer
Uanterl sorle lla ehva fifedtrne wni niintsdooc adn aer ont no a eamt. Rof eemalxp: Tsejer nwis if yeht aer tdove tuo rgnuid a rital
wiki.article.standard.briefing.title: Nebifrgi
wiki.article.standard.briefing.text:
Nebifrgi is tlcliyayp eth frtis eapsh fo eth agme.

Rgnuid nebifrgi, aelrysp:
* Tlcliyayp dear eth miithndg lunmaa ot gfireu tuo ohw hreti loer kwsro.
* If yeht ehva emit, ihst is salo a ogdo trnoupoipty ot rsatt initrgw an ibila or rsatt ighinntk fo plsna rof eth agme.
* If yeht aer veil, yma salo try ot salo lnera ohw ta astel eon wiento loer kwsro os yeht nca pnertde ot eb ttha loer.
* Srspe eth satf fwardor ntbout ni eth opt tlfe fo eth crnsee eocn yeht aer dneo rndaeig eth lunmaa, ni rdeor ot rsatt eth agme kqcurei.

Eth miithndg lunmaa sha a slti fo lla sorle adn hreti iltsiabie, os ti is dmeemocndre ot kate ihst emit ot dear pu no yoru loer adn yan eohtr nnmiioftaro you lliw deen ot ypal leveceftyfi.

Eth frtis eapsh eafrt nebifrgi is Skdu.
wiki.article.standard.night.title: Ihtng
wiki.article.standard.night.text:
Eth Ihtng eapsh ocsem eafrt Skdu. Ti is tlcliyayp hwne msot aelrysp ehva ot seu hreti loer iltsiabie.

Rof eemalxp:
- Heca ihtng, eth tcevetdei eoohscs a rpelay ot asgtetviine
- Heca ihtng ecexpt eth frtis, eth rpelay ihwt eth inctadesy ugn nca escooh ot hsoot a rpelay.
- Msot eohtr sorle salo seu hreti iltsiabie ta ihtng as well.

Eafrt vgiahn emda hreti niceelstso rgnuid ihtng, eth ruestsl fo a lre'spya iltsiabie adn eth ihnsgt ttha nahppe ot temh lliw eb sohnw ta eth rsatt fo eth tenx eapsh, Rytoauib.
wiki.article.standard.obituary.title: Rytoauib
wiki.article.standard.obituary.text:
Rytoauib ocsem eafrt eth nteevs fo ihtng.

Rgnuid eth rytoauib eapsh, rneeeyov is told owh ided, nloag ihwt eth loer adn ibila fo oesth owh ided.
Rgnuid rytoauib, aelrysp atnnoc kspae ot heca eohtr, ciwhh smaek ti a ogdo trnoupoipty rof aelrysp ot adpeut hreti ibila teon pgae ihwt eth nnmiioftaro yeht lerdnae rgnuid eth agme.

Rof eemalxp:
- A tcevetdei owh lerdnae ttha @5 is ispuiossuc no ihtng 1, ulwdo tpu ttha nnmiioftaro ni hreti ibila.
- A rpelay owh swa tekacatd adn eectdprot ulwdo teon ttha ni hreti ibila as well.
- A rpelay owh swa eordobcelkl hodsul teon ttha as well, os eohtr aelrysp 'terna ispuiossuc wyh yeht v'tnhae ontgte yan nnmiioftaro.
- An veil rpelay dsnee ot fake eth nnmiioftaro yeht ivceeedr, os rgnuid ihst emit yeht ehva eth trnoupoipty ot cmeo pu ihwt a plan adn ewitr hreti fake nnmiioftaro ni hreti ibila ot floo eohtr aelrysp.

Eafrt rytoauib, eth ayd atrsst ihwt eth indsocsusi eapsh.
wiki.article.standard.discussion.title: Indsocsusi
wiki.article.standard.discussion.text:
Eth indsocsusi eapsh ocsem eafrt rytoauib.

Rgnuid indsocsusi, aelrysp csiusds eth nnmiioftaro yeht lerdnae adn try ot dnfi tuo owh eth inctadesy, isndef, adn utcl aer.
Aelrysp lliw ksa heca eohtr ot mailc. Ihst nmase yeht atnw ot wonk eth nnmiioftaro ttha eth eohtr rpelay lerdnae.
Msot aelrysp dnes hreti ibila ni ahct rgnuid ihst eapsh ni rdeor ot hersa hreti wolhe mailc lycetffinie. Aelrysp utihwot a ppdraere ibila dten ot esme ispuiossuc, os tis' rvey iapnotrtm ot ehva eon ppdraere, no tteram owh you aer.

Eafrt indsocsusi ocsem eth inmntanooi eapsh.
wiki.article.standard.nomination.title: Inmntanooi
wiki.article.standard.nomination.text:
Eth inmntanooi eapsh ocsem eafrt eth indsocsusi eapsh.

Rgnuid inmntanooi, aelrysp nca evto eohtr aelrysp no ot railt ni rdeor ot eeeuctx temh.
Eth sebt ayw rof oswtien ot klil inctadesy meremsb is ot seu hreti evto:
- Eenv if you 'terna atincre emoones is veil, otnvgi temh oont railt as a teatrh lliw tfone nnvoecci temh ot igve nnmiioftaro (or, if yeht reew veil, ot try ot cmeo pu ihwt a fdeenes).
- Tlcliyayp, if rome ntha fhla fo eth iigvln aelrysp evto rof eon rpelay, ttha rpelay is tpu no railt adn inevg a osytmtnie eapsh ot ianexpl vehsetmsel.

If eterh eran’t oguhne oesvt ot rsatt a railt ni emit, eth agme sipks lrytecdi ot eth skdu eapsh.
wiki.article.standard.adjournment.title: Aretdnjmoun
wiki.article.standard.adjournment.text: Eth Aretdnjmoun eapsh ocsem eafrt inmntanooi ynol if eterh swa no rpelay maneontid. Ti aserlcpe eth railt ttha swa smieds.
wiki.article.standard.testimony.title: Osytmtnie
wiki.article.standard.testimony.text:
Eth Osytmtnie eapsh uosrcc hwne a rpelay is tdove ot railt rgnuid inmntanooi.

Eth rpelay no railt:
- Is eth ynol rpelay dleowla ot kspae adn ahct rgnuid ihst eapsh.
- Hodsul llkeiy mailc, dnes hreti ibila adn ysa ahwt hreti loer is if yeht tndo' atnw ot eb tdove tuo.
- Eietmsmos, pieslceyal if yeht aer veil, hodsul try ot tpu rpsseuer no theonra rpelay ot try ot get temh tdove tuo indsate.

Tymrtaoinpl, egbni tdove tuo seod ont amek a rpelay sleo, adn eietmsmos eth sebt uocers fo cnaoti is ot evto tuo a ogdo rpelay.

Eafrt a lre'spya osytmtnie ocsem eth tedgumjen eapsh.
wiki.article.standard.judgement.title: Tedgumjen
wiki.article.standard.judgement.text:
Eth Tedgumjen eapsh fwsolol eth osytmtnie eapsh.

Rgnuid eth Tedgumjen eapsh:

- Rneeeyov oesvt ehwerht eth rpelay no railt is oitnncen or uytigl
- If rome aelrysp evto uytigl ntha oitnncen, eth rpelay no railt lliw eb inevg a lniaf wdsor eapsh as eon slta trnoupoipty ot kspae.
- If eth rpelay no railt is indsate tdove oitnncen, eth agme lliw trurne ot eth inmntanooi eapsh if eterh aer rome alisrt, ihtsoeewr ti lliw oecrped ot skdu.
wiki.article.standard.finalWords.title: Lniaf Wdsor

Eth Lniaf Wdsor eapsh uosrcc eafrt a Jtmnegdu eapsh hwne eth rpelay no railt is ndouf uytigl.

Rgnuid lniaf wdsor:
- Lla aelrysp nca kspae.
- Eth rpelay no railt owh is batuo ot die nca hersa hreti slta uhtothgs.

Ta eth ned fo lniaf wdsor, eth rpelay no railt is llikde yb uictnoxee, adn eth agme pdcesoer ot skdu.
